@startuml seq-ui-core-interaction
title ClubGear — UI/Core-Interaktion (Member + SelfService + Account)

actor "Admin / Verwalter" as Admin
actor "Mitglied" as Member
actor "Browser" as Browser
participant "MembersController" as MembersCtrl
participant "SelfServiceController" as SelfCtrl
participant "AccountController" as AccountCtrl
participant "IMemberFeatureService\n(MemberFeatureService)" as MemberSvc
participant "ISelfServiceFeatureService\n(SelfServiceFeatureService)" as SelfSvc
participant "IAccountFeatureService\n(AccountFeatureService)" as AccountSvc
participant "ApplicationDbContext" as DB

Admin -> Browser : Navigiert zu /Members/Index
Browser -> MembersCtrl : GET /Members/Index?search&status
MembersCtrl -> MemberSvc : GetListAsync(search)
MemberSvc -> DB : Query Members + Segmente
DB --> MemberSvc : Member-Liste
MemberSvc --> MembersCtrl : Liste
MembersCtrl --> Browser : View(Index)

Admin -> Browser : Speichert Member-Edit
Browser -> MembersCtrl : POST /Members/Edit/{id}
MembersCtrl -> MemberSvc : UpdateAsync(member, actor)
MemberSvc -> DB : UPDATE Members / MemberAddresses
MembersCtrl --> Browser : Redirect /Members/Index + Feedback

Member -> Browser : Oeffnet Selfservice
Browser -> SelfCtrl : GET /SelfService/Index
SelfCtrl -> SelfSvc : GetDashboardAsync(User)
SelfSvc -> DB : Resolve verknuepftes Memberprofil
SelfCtrl --> Browser : View(Index)

Member -> Browser : Aktualisiert eigenes Profil
Browser -> SelfCtrl : POST /SelfService/Profile
SelfCtrl -> SelfSvc : UpdateProfileAsync(User, model)
SelfSvc -> DB : UPDATE Members
SelfCtrl --> Browser : Redirect /SelfService/Profile

Browser -> AccountCtrl : GET /Account/Login
Browser -> AccountCtrl : POST /Account/Login
AccountCtrl -> AccountSvc : LoginAsync(email, password)
AccountSvc -> DB : Identity-Login + User-Abgleich
AccountCtrl --> Browser : Redirect /SelfService oder returnUrl

Browser -> AccountCtrl : POST /Account/Logout
AccountCtrl -> AccountSvc : LogoutAsync()
AccountCtrl --> Browser : Redirect /Home/Index

@enduml
